{"tid":1595663,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"強烈建議林奠去全港18區對話","createTime":"2019-09-26T07:17:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-26T07:21:41.000Z","uid":134093,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4b6cc178643f356731c9350b4760e0437a0b19cc","tid":1595663,"uid":134093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T07:17:42.000Z","msg":"衞生署宣布，鑑於灣仔區的情況，以下服務單位將於下午4時提早關閉，受影響的預約人士會獲安排另約診症時間。<br />\n<br />\n1. 灣仔牙科診所<br />\n2. 麥理浩牙科中心（包括政府牙科診所及鄧肇堅學童牙科診所）<br />\n3. 鄧志昂母嬰健康院<br />\n4. 灣仔男性社會衞生科診所<br />\n5. 灣仔女性社會衞生科診所<br />\n6. 灣仔胸肺科診所<br />\n7. 香港公務員診所<br />\n8. 旅遊健康中心（香港）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n對話未開始，先有8間診所暫停服務<br />\n學校被逼提早放學<br />\n餐廳亦提早關門<br />\n附近馬路亦封閉，停泊兩旁汽車被拖走<br />\n<br />\n未對話先戒嚴<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">有警察嘅地方就會亂<br />\n有林鄭嘅地方就會戒嚴</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">建議特首媽媽落多幾次區<br />\n睇下民意會點</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n諗起都開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec368c2c313705eb1f025e7567f85c01946e9c42","tid":1595663,"uid":134093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T07:18:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d27fd2637f2bd8392898280c4b3faa3c8561f092","tid":1595663,"uid":7840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T07:20:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1e156c32a082245ff4ea273cbd830512da23a7fe","tid":1595663,"uid":258770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T07:20:47.000Z","msg":"其實佢真心想了解民意既話應該親自black bloc落場一齊起下路障捱下棍食下催淚彈"},{"pid":"b23b80adaeda81c6c209d5838e5db5400310ee4b","tid":1595663,"uid":315851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T07:21:41.000Z","msg":"訓左幾耐，香港一早得番17區<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}